  "text": "Found all key files for Ingress API handling across v1beta1 and v1 in kubernetes/kubernetes:\n\n**Conversion functions:**\n- `pkg/apis/networking/v1beta1/conversion.go` \u2014 Manual conversion between networking.k8s.io/v1beta1 and internal types (IngressBackend, IngressSpec with ServiceName/ServicePort \u2194 Service.Name/Service.Port mapping)\n- `pkg/apis/networking/v1beta1/zz_generated.conversion.go` \u2014 Auto-generated conversion for networking v1beta1\n- `pkg/apis/networking/v1/zz_generated.conversion.go` \u2014 Auto-generated conversion for networking v1\n- `pkg/apis/extensions/v1beta1/conversion.go` \u2014 Manual conversion between extensions/v1beta1 and internal types (identical Ingress Backend/Spec conversion logic)\n- `pkg/apis/extensions/v1beta1/zz_generated.conversion.go` \u2014 Auto-generated conversion for extensions v1beta1 (includes all Ingress types)\n\n**Validation (pathType became required):**\n- `pkg/apis/networking/validation/validation.go` \u2014 Contains `validateHTTPIngressPath` which enforces `pathType` as required (line 428-429), `IngressValidationOptions` struct, and `ValidateIngressCreate`/`ValidateIngressUpdate`\n\n**Defaults (pathType defaulting for v1beta1):**\n- `pkg/apis/networking/v1beta1/defaults.go` \u2014 `SetDefaults_HTTPIngressPath` defaults pathType to `ImplementationSpecific` for networking v1beta1\n- `pkg/apis/extensions/v1beta1/defaults.go` \u2014 Same defaulting for extensions v1beta1\n\n**Storage version / registry:**\n- `pkg/apis/networking/types.go` \u2014 Internal Ingress type definitions including PathType\n- `pkg/registry/networking/ingress/strategy.go` \u2014 Strategy handling for Ingress CRUD (references both extensions/v1beta1, networking/v1beta1, and networking/v1 API versions in ResetFields)\n- `pkg/registry/networking/ingress/storage/storage.go` \u2014 REST storage for Ingress\n- `pkg/registry/networking/rest/storage_settings.go` \u2014 Wires up Ingress storage into v1 and v1beta1 API group versions\n- `pkg/kubeapiserver/default_storage_factory_builder.go` \u2014 Configures cohabitating resources (networking.ingresses + extensions.ingresses share storage) and storage prefixes",
